Facultas Utrimque  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uasaphdiamondwolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Asaph Diamondwolf</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/01 6:32:31 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1375.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.greypathfinders.com/face_nime.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re</span><hr size=1> So if we are so gimped, and you wanted to go with the most difficult class, why become frustrated when achieveing your goal?<br>
