 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uryken.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ryken</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/01 11:48:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1375.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> archers</span><hr size=1> Archers stealth as an ability, not a skill.<br>
