60 Gnomish Rogue, Bristlebane Server</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugugustp.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gugus TP</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/19/01 9:54:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1375.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: why cant we....</span><hr size=1> I think that archers need a little nerf. Can you afirm today that PvP is balanced really? No i dont think so. Archers have too many advantages compared to the others. Dont tell me they are vulnerable in melee, cause only a dumb archer ever finds himself meleeing in pvp (they stay stealthed all the time and only an assassin type has a chance to approach them). Then they can shoot from far for an insane damage (compared to assassin types again), and have better armor. The two last times i died in pvp were archers: Once i died in 2 arrows, then i was shoot for 700dmg and got insta killed. Even versus a blue con (and maybe green?) I cant do that...And i gotta position myself (knowing that 50% of the time ur stab fails cause the guy turned himself right when u attacked)!! Our critical just sux compared to theirs, and this is not fair cause it s much harder for us than for them.<br>
<br>
