<br>
Also, the only people in my guild that constantly solo past level 40 are Hunters.  My guild will get a group together to hunt for Exp, and the ONLY class that ever says, &quot;I think I am going to go solo now&quot; are the Hunters.  Sometimes while fighting con yellows while teamed with 1 Hunter I won't even get to take a swing because the critter is dead before it gets to me.  Once in a while this happens with con orange critters.  If the Hunter picks the right target they can solo easily past level 40.<br>
<br>
